        "2159": {
          "vnum": 2159,
          "name": "Opposite a Narrow Channel",
          "description": "You have come opposite a narrow channel which cuts deeply into the coast. The channel is widest at its mouth causing the waves to funnel into its length with incredible force. The way the water smashes against the jagged rocks which populate the channel suggest that it would be a big mistake to enter.",
