        "2162": {
          "vnum": 2162,
          "name": "The Deep, Azure Sea",
          "description": "The water beneath you seems iridescent and flecked with foam. To the east you see the beach disappear from view and to the west you think you glimpse the tops of islands peeking from the clouds. You feel as if you are getting closer to land.",
