          "name": "The Open Sea",
          "description": "You are far from the sight of land. The endless expanse of water and the constant tossing of the waves make it impossible to move in a straight line. If fortune smiles on you, it may be that your wandering will bring you closer to the coast. You feel somewhat dizzy and confused.",
